description: A collection of circles in a large cylindrical formation intersected by a thin rectangular formation; there is also a rounded triangular formation at the top of the cylindrical formation. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a red triangle at the top of the cylindrical formation and a yellowish-orange triangle on the left side below where the cylindrical formation is intersected by the rectangular formation.
